<plot>As an immigrant to America at the outset of WWII, a young German woman finds herself a target of persecution and growing hostility. Some members of her community go so far as to openly accuse her of being a Nazi spy or sympathizer. Even her newlywed husband, a US Army Air Corps Officer, begins to doubt her loyalty. But it is her faith that sustains her to a suspenseful conclusion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?555470</url></doc>
